==== Known Risks

    - Fludrocortisone: Hypokalemia, hypertension, edema
    - Midodrine: Supine hypertension, urinary retention
    - Ivabradine: Bradycardia, visual disturbances
    - LDN: Vivid dreams, transient sleep disturbance
    - Multiple supplements: GI upset, interactions

